{
  "id": "adv_event_2406_01_05",
  "title": "待ってるよ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブバトルから数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several days after the live battle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.3200001479,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4066.6666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます\nお二人とも早いですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning.\nYou two are early.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.5666667302,
      "endTime": 9.5019955,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "完成した新曲のデモを聴いたら、じっとしてられなくて\nいつもより早めにスタジオに来ちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I couldn’t sit still after listening to the demo of the completed new song‚\nso I came to the studio earlier than usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.7086620808,
      "endTime": 16.303197240899998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "分かります。私もあの歌を聴いてから\n振り付けのアイデアが次々とわいてきています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. I’ve also been getting\none choreography idea after another ever since I heard that song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.5165305933,
      "endTime": 23.403265365,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "私達の曲に込めたい想いがうまく伝わって\nとても素敵な歌詞になったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our feelings that we wanted to put into our song were conveyed well‚\nand the lyrics turned out really lovely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.6165985267,
      "endTime": 29.9719044844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "眩しい太陽の光とは違う……そっと道を照らして\n大事なことに気付かせてくれる優しい光……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s different from the dazzling sunlight… a gentle light that softly illuminates the path\nand makes you realize important things…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1852379322,
      "endTime": 40.0281179905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "静かに寄り添う優しさと、迷いを吹き飛ばす勇気と強さ\n……月のテンペストらしさが込められた、いい曲です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The gentleness that quietly draws near‚ the courage and strength to blow away hesitation…\n…It’s a good song that embodies the essence of Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2147845428,
      "endTime": 49.420521466000004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "最高の曲に負けないように\n私達も最高のパフォーマンスをしないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have to give the best performance possible\nso as to not lose to this amazing song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6271879991,
      "endTime": 55.2226982912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "決戦の日まで残り僅か。この短期間でパフォーマンスの\n完成度をどこまで高められるかが勝負よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s only a little time left until the decisive battle. The key to victory is\nhow much we can improve the quality of the performance in this short time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.416031472,
      "endTime": 63.3133558433,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "時間との勝負ですね\n実際、かなり厳しいですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a race against time.\nIndeed‚ it’s quite difficult…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.5266891957,
      "endTime": 69.4514736653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "今日だって芽衣ちゃんとすずちゃんはお仕事で\n夜にならないと五人揃って練習出来ませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even today‚ Mei-chan and Suzu-chan are working‚\nso we can’t practice with all five of us until tonight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.66480697,
      "endTime": 76.6411561331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "それでもやるしかないよ！\nみんなで力を合わせて頑張ろう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even so‚ we have to do it!\nLet’s all work hard together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8278226854,
      "endTime": 81.732425976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。今は出来ることをやりましょう\nまずは新曲の振り付けを完成させて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Let’s do what we can for now.\nFirst‚ let’s finish the choreography for the new song――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9190926713,
      "endTime": 89.0547843141,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7447.573995399992
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "おっはようございまーす！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning～！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.1814566137,
      "endTime": 91.4405041219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "さくら！？\nそれに雫も……どうしてあなた達がここに？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "さくら！？\nSakura!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.5538358768,
      "endTime": 97.5212510189,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "新曲のデモ……私達も聴かせてもらった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We listened… to the demo of the new song…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.7212510189,
      "endTime": 101.97803097570001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "それがすっごく良くて、琴乃ちゃん達が歌う姿を\n想像したら、いても立ってもいられなくなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was so good‚ and when I imagined you singing it‚ Kotono-chan‚\nI couldn’t just stand by and do nothing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.1879176856,
      "endTime": 110.4881923438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "それで私達の様子を見に来たの？\nその行動力はさくららしいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you came to check up on us?\nThat proactiveness is so like you‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.6881921531,
      "endTime": 119.30692250739999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ～。でも来たのは私だけじゃないよ\nこれから新曲の振り付けを作るんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe～。 But I’m not the only one who came.\nYou’re going to make the choreography for the new song now‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.5135892313,
      "endTime": 128.2421609322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "そこで助っ人のスーパーコーチを連れて来ました！\nじゃーん、先生、お願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I brought a super coach to help!\nTa-da! Teacher‚ please!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.4554940939,
      "endTime": 136.9014806509,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8827.686611500014
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、変な呼び込みしないでよ\n恥ずかしいじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ don’t introduce me in a weird way!\nIt’s embarrassing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.1148138125,
      "endTime": 143.1165373881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "コーチって……怜ちゃんが私達を手伝ってくれるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Coach… Rei-chan’s going to help us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.3165373881,
      "endTime": 148.40254622289999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "月ストの新曲、私も聴いたけど凄く良かったわ\nぜひ振り付けを作るのを手伝わせてもらえないかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I listened to Moon Tempest’s new song too‚ and it was really good.\nI’d love to help with making the choreography‚ if that’s okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.6092127561,
      "endTime": 158.39456431859998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "私はみんなのダンスをばっちり撮影する……\n振り付けの確認と分析は任せて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll perfectly film everyone’s dancing…\nLeave the choreography checking and analysis to me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.5945641279,
      "endTime": 165.5992808104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんと雫ちゃんだけじゃないよ\n私や遙子ちゃん、千紗ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not just Rei-chan and Shizuku-chan!\nMe‚ Haruko-chan‚ Chisa-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.7945641279,
      "endTime": 171.8957206487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "それに他の星見プロのみんなも月ストを手伝うから\n力になれることがあればなんでも言ってね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and everyone else from Hoshimi Pro is going to help Moon Tempest too.\nSo if there’s anything we can do to help‚ just say the word!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.0890538294,
      "endTime": 180.0780334552,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、これは月ストの勝負なのに\nみんなを巻き込むなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But this is Moon Tempest’s battle…\nTo involve everyone is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.2647000074,
      "endTime": 186.1290763616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2406_01_05-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "水くさいわね。私達がスリクスと対戦した時も\n月ストはずっとサポートしてくれたじゃない",
